column2: Election Commission of Malaysia (SPR), Tindak Malaysia (2023), Attorney General Chambers, The Star, Undi.info. Refer to individual State Candidate Age Source file for more details

Correction was made for spelling error of Independent in Kedah. There may be discrepancies for the age of candidates as there is no official data released for the attribute.There are many missing data points for age attribute for candidates. If year/date of birth is found, age of candidate shown here is the age of the candidate at the end of 31/12/2018 (with an error range of +/-1 year). There was a United Sabah Alliance (GSB) which consists of SAPP, STAR (Sabah), PHRS and PPRS. However, there seat clashes between PHRS, STAR (Sabah) and PPRS. For this file,these component parties were divided into various Other Party columns. TindakMalaysia Network Services PLT is not responsible for any errors or ommissions arising from the original data or its derivatives.
